<li><i><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young:_American_Moses" title="Brigham Young: American Moses">Brigham Young: American Moses</a></i>, by <a href="/wiki/Leonard_J._Arrington" title="Leonard J. Arrington">Leonard J. Arrington</a>, University of Illinois Press, (1986)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Blood_of_the_Prophets:_Brigham_Young_and_the_Massacre_at_Mountain_Meadows" title="Blood of the Prophets: Brigham Young and the Massacre at Mountain Meadows" class="mw-redirect">Blood of the Prophets: Brigham Young and the Massacre at Mountain Meadows</a></i> by <a href="/wiki/Will_Bagley" title="Will Bagley">Will Bagley</a> (2002)</li>
