<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYoung1857c"><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">Young, Brigham</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-05"><a href="/wiki/July_5" title="July 5">July 5</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1857" title="1857">1857c</a>), <a href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/JournalOfDiscourses3,2375" class="external text" title="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/JournalOfDiscourses3,2375" rel="nofollow">"True Happiness—Fruits of Not Following Counsel—Popular Prejudice Against the Mormons—The Coming Army—Punishment of Evildoers"</a>, in Calkin, Asa, <i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses_Delivered_by_President_Brigham_Young,_His_Two_Counsellors,_the_Twelve_Apostles,_and_Others" title="Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, the Twelve Apostles, and Others" class="mw-redirect">Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, the Twelve Apostles, and Others</a></i>, <b>5</b>, Liverpool: Asa Calkin, 1858, pp.&#160;1–6</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=True+Happiness%E2%80%94Fruits+of+Not+Following+Counsel%E2%80%94Popular+Prejudice+Against+the+Mormons%E2%80%94The+Coming+Army%E2%80%94Punishment+of+Evildoers&amp;rft.atitle=%5B%5BJournal+of+Discourses+Delivered+by+President+Brigham+Young%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+the+Twelve+Apostles%2C+and+Others%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft.au=Young%2C+Brigham&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BJuly+5%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1857%5D%5Dc&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B1%E2%80%936&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pub=Asa+Calkin&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mountain_Meadows_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYoung1857d"><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">Young, Brigham</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-26"><a href="/wiki/July_26" title="July 26">July 26</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1857" title="1857">1857d</a>), <a href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/JournalOfDiscourses3,2304" class="external text" title="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/u?/JournalOfDiscourses3,2304" rel="nofollow">"Nebuchadnezzar's Dream—Opposition of Men and Devils to the Latter-Day Kingdom—Governmental Breach of the Utah Mail Contract"</a>, in Calkin, Asa, <i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses_Delivered_by_President_Brigham_Young,_His_Two_Counsellors,_the_Twelve_Apostles,_and_Others" title="Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, the Twelve Apostles, and Others" class="mw-redirect">Journal of Discourses Delivered by President Brigham Young, His Two Counsellors, the Twelve Apostles, and Others</a></i>, <b>5</b>, Liverpool: Asa Calkin, 1858, pp.&#160;72–78</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Nebuchadnezzar%27s+Dream%E2%80%94Opposition+of+Men+and+Devils+to+the+Latter-Day+Kingdom%E2%80%94Governmental+Breach+of+the+Utah+Mail+Contract&amp;rft.atitle=%5B%5BJournal+of+Discourses+Delivered+by+President+Brigham+Young%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+the+Twelve+Apostles%2C+and+Others%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft.au=Young%2C+Brigham&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BJuly+26%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1857%5D%5Dd&amp;rft.volume=5&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B72%E2%80%9378&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pub=Asa+Calkin&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mountain_Meadows_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYoung1857a">Young, Brigham (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-05"><a href="/wiki/August_5" title="August 5">August 5</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1857" title="1857">1857a</a>), <i><a href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cgi-bin/docviewer.exe?CISOROOT=/NCMP1847-1877&amp;CISOPTR=2905" class="external text" title="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cgi-bin/docviewer.exe?CISOROOT=/NCMP1847-1877&amp;CISOPTR=2905" rel="nofollow">Proclamation by the Governor</a></i>, Salt Lake City: Utah Territory<span class="printonly">, <a href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cgi-bin/docviewer.exe?CISOROOT=/NCMP1847-1877&amp;CISOPTR=2905" class="external free" title="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cgi-bin/docviewer.exe?CISOROOT=/NCMP1847-1877&amp;CISOPTR=2905" rel="nofollow">http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cgi-bin/docviewer.exe?CISOROOT=/NCMP1847-1877&amp;CISOPTR=2905</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Proclamation+by+the+Governor&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft.au=Young%2C+Brigham&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BAugust+5%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1857%5D%5Da&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft.pub=Utah+Territory&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fcontentdm.lib.byu.edu%2Fcgi-bin%2Fdocviewer.exe%3FCISOROOT%3D%2FNCMP1847-1877%26CISOPTR%3D2905&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mountain_Meadows_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYoung1869"><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">Young, Brigham</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1867-04-07"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="04-07"><a href="/wiki/April_7" title="April 7">April 7</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1867" title="1867">1867</a></span>), <a href="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cdm4/document.php?CISOROOT=/JournalOfDiscourses3&amp;CISOPTR=10004&amp;REC=4" class="external text" title="http://contentdm.lib.byu.edu/cdm4/document.php?CISOROOT=/JournalOfDiscourses3&amp;CISOPTR=10004&amp;REC=4" rel="nofollow">"Word of wisdom"</a>, in <a href="/wiki/George_D._Watt" title="George D. Watt">Watt, G.D.</a>, <i><a href="/wiki/Journal_of_Discourses_by_Brigham_Young,_President_of_the_Church_of_Jesus_Christ_of_Latter-day_Saints,_His_Two_Counsellors,_and_the_Twelve_Apostles" title="Journal of Discourses by Brigham Young, President of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, His Two Counsellors, and the Twelve Apostles" class="mw-redirect">Journal of Discourses by Brigham Young, President of the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, His Two Counsellors, and the Twelve Apostles</a></i>, <b>12</b>, Liverpool: S.W. Richards, 1869, pp.&#160;27</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Word+of+wisdom&amp;rft.atitle=%5B%5BJournal+of+Discourses+by+Brigham+Young%2C+President+of+the+Church+of+Jesus+Christ+of+Latter-day+Saints%2C+His+Two+Counsellors%2C+and+the+Twelve+Apostles%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft.au=Young%2C+Brigham&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BApril+7%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1867%5D%5D&amp;rft.volume=12&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B27&amp;rft.place=Liverpool&amp;rft.pub=S.W.+Richards&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mountain_Meadows_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYoung"><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">Young, Brigham</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1875-07-30"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="07-30"><a href="/wiki/July_30" title="July 30">July 30</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1875" title="1875">1875</a></span>), "<a href="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,737649" class="external text" title="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,737649" rel="nofollow">Deposition, People v. Lee</a>", <i><a href="/wiki/Deseret_News" title="Deseret News">Deseret News</a></i> (Salt Lake City) <b>24</b> (27): 8, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1875-08-04"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="08-04"><a href="/wiki/August_4" title="August 4">August 4</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1875" title="1875">1875</a></span><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,737649" class="external free" title="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,737649" rel="nofollow">http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,737649</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Deposition%2C+People+v.+Lee&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BDeseret+News%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft.au=Young%2C+Brigham&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BJuly+30%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1875%5D%5D&amp;rft.volume=24&amp;rft.issue=27&amp;rft.pages=8&amp;rft.place=Salt+Lake+City&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.lib.utah.edu%2Fu%3F%2Fdeseretnews3%2C737649&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mountain_Meadows_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span>.</li>
<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="" id="CITEREFYoung"><a href="/wiki/Brigham_Young" title="Brigham Young">Young, Brigham</a> (<span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1877-04-30"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="04-30"><a href="/wiki/April_30" title="April 30">April 30</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1877" title="1877">1877</a></span>), "<a href="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,150800" class="external text" title="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,150800" rel="nofollow">Interview with Brigham Young</a>", <i><a href="/wiki/Deseret_News" title="Deseret News">Deseret News</a></i> <b>26</b> (16): 242–43, <span class="mw-formatted-date" title="1877-05-23"><span class="mw-formatted-date" title="05-23"><a href="/wiki/May_23" title="May 23">May 23</a></span>, <a href="/wiki/1877" title="1877">1877</a></span><span class="printonly">, <a href="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,150800" class="external free" title="http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,150800" rel="nofollow">http://udn.lib.utah.edu/u?/deseretnews3,150800</a></span></cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Interview+with+Brigham+Young&amp;rft.jtitle=%5B%5BDeseret+News%5D%5D&amp;rft.aulast=Young&amp;rft.aufirst=Brigham&amp;rft.au=Young%2C+Brigham&amp;rft.date=%5B%5BApril+30%5D%5D%2C+%5B%5B1877%5D%5D&amp;rft.volume=26&amp;rft.issue=16&amp;rft.pages=242%E2%80%9343&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fudn.lib.utah.edu%2Fu%3F%2Fdeseretnews3%2C150800&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mountain_Meadows_massacre"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
</ul>
